以上有期徒刑；致重傷者，處三年以上十年以下有期徒刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/110%2c%e8%8b%97%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c757%2c20220210%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,110,苗交簡,757,20220210,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"苗交簡","JNO":"757","JDATE":"20220210","JTITLE":"公共危險"}